script params
    Calculates the optimal miniaturization parameters for a graph

    Parameters
    ----------
    path_metrics
        path to the .json file containing the metrics of the graph
    dir_output
        output directory where to store the calculated weights
    n_changes
        number of changes proposed at each step
    n_samples
        number of times the experiment is repeated
    n_steps
        number of iterations for each experiment

    
script miniaturize
    Creates the miniature of a graph using Parallel Tempering

    Parameters
    ----------
    path_metrics
        path to the .json file containing the metrics of the graph
    path_params
        path to the .json file containing the miniaturization parameters for the graph
    n_changes
        number of changes proposed at each step
    n_steps
        number of total miniaturization steps
    n_substeps
        

script simulate_sir
    Simulates the Susceptible-infected-recovered compartmental model on a graph

script simulate_degroot
    Simulates the degroot learning model on a graph

script qois_sir
    Calculates the quantities of interest of an sir simulation

script qois_degroot
    Calculates the quantities of interest of a degroot simulation 

script visualization_sir
    Plots the compartment trajectories of the sir model
    
script visualization_degroot
    Plots the trajectories of the beliefs of each individual
